column5: Well, if I had a fishing partner that looked like thet I'll bet my wife would get a lot more interested in fishing all of a sudden!
Great job guys!! keep em coming!

At the Toronto Sportsmans Show I had a chat with  the owners of a brand new magazine, based here in Ontario.  They  offered up 3 subscriptions to me to help promote thier start up!  If you have a chance, visit the contest form and help me show them the power of our community... plus ya might win a subscription... and if ya cant wait.. ya can always subscribe.  CLICK HERE TO ENTER THE CONTEST!
Been a while since I had bikinis like those on board. Thanks TJ.
